I don't know.

186
00:16:11.970 --> 00:16:14.486
The reason that I asked you to stop by...

187
00:16:14.510 --> 00:16:18.036
Have you finished the report
on sheriff Nichols's cleaning?

188
00:16:18.060 --> 00:16:19.246
Almost.

189
00:16:19.270 --> 00:16:20.826
